    "It is worth noting that both UltraChat and UltraFeedback were curated specifically for the chat completion task.",
    "KTO and CPO don't require SFT.",
    "The findings presented in Figure 1 indicate that skipping the SFT phase resulted in Mistral+IPO and Mistral+DPO performing poorly in the dialogue system, as they attained lower scores compared to SFT.",
